      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Chop your <strong>paneer </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped paneer</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min, turning once halfway until beginning to turn golden</p>",
