      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan with the paneer and cook for 10 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and<strong> tomato wedges </strong>and cook for 1 min further, stirring until fully combined</p>",
