    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then add it to the pan with a small splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and cook, covered, for 1-2 min or until wilted</p><p>Once wilted, remove the pan from the heat and stir your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> through the sauce – this is your <strong>chilli paneer masala</strong></p>",
